# Build artifacts and caches we never want shipped into the image.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.git
**/.idea
**/.vscode
**/.claude
**/.DS_Store
**/coverage
**/test-results
**/.yarn/install-state.gz
**/.yarn/cache/.cleaning
**/*.log

# Local runtime state — must come from a mounted volume, not the image.
**/database
**/media

# Top-level scaffolding files that aren't part of the build.
Dockerfile
docker-compose.yml
.dockerignore
README*.md
CLAUDE.md
